      <bioghist id="aspace_76b70e670c25ec1bfe22b44ee1f7eff3">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Anya Montiel (Yale MA, PhD) is an art historian, curator, and historian specializing in Native American art, arts and crafts, American history, and museum studies.</p>  
      </bioghist>
